      info home http://www.procmail.org/
      desc 'mail sorter
The procmail and formail mail processing package
can be used to create mail-servers, mailing lists,
sort your incoming mail into separate folders/files
(real convenient when subscribing to one or more
mailing lists or for prioritising your mail),
preprocess your mail, start any programs upon mail
arrival (e.g. to generate different chimes on your
workstation for different types of mail) or
selectively forward certain incoming mail automatically.'

build(){
sed -i 's:LOCKINGTEST=__defaults__:LOCKINGTEST=/tmp:' Makefile
make init &&
make install BASENAME=$DESTDIR
}
